reviews.text: Quiet place for relax with average food.
Pretty cozy place for people that likes Japanese stuff lol

Nice Japanese style maid cafe in Mong Kok area. Girls were polite and funny, just as their role is supposed to be. You are not allowed to take photos with the maids unless you pay a fee, and the cafe itself is not really pretty enough to take photos. The food was okay and drinks too. Not much of an active atmosphere in early afternoon.
